1) Replace all of the following placeholders with actual values

		%PROJECT_GROUP_ID%
		%PROJECT_ARTIFACT_ID%
		%PROJECT_NAME%
		%REPO_OWNER%
		%REPO_NAME%
		%BINTRAY_USERNAME%

   in all of the following files:

		pom.xml
		.github/workflows-template/*.yaml
		.github/workflows-template/*.sh

2) Add the following secrets under GitHub -> Project -> Settings -> Secrets:

		GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN
		BINTRAY_API_KEY

   The `GITHUB_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN` must have the full repo scope and the full packages scope.
   The `BINTRAY_API_KEY` must belong to the above mentioned `%BINTRAY_USERNAME%`.

3) Rename the directory `.github/workflows-template` to `.github/workflows`.

4) Add a new package with the name `%REPO_NAME%` under Bintray -> %REPO_OWNER% -> repositories -> maven-repo.

5) Afterwards this `FIRST STEPS` file can be deleted.

6) Commit and push the changes. You are ready to go ...
